/li>\n<li><b>Skup si\u0119 na rynku Beauty i FMCG.<\/b> Zastosuj podobne strategie w bran\u017cy kosmetycznej lub FMCG, gdzie konkurencja mo\u017ce by\u0107 wysoka, a odpowiednie stawki mog\u0105 pom\u00f3c wyr\u00f3\u017cni\u0107 Twoje produkty.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Podsumowuj\u0105c, skuteczne zarz\u0105dzanie bud\u017cetem reklamowym w kategorii suplement\u00f3w wymaga przemy\u015blanej strategii i ci\u0105g\u0142ego testowania. Pami\u0119taj, \u017ce kluczem jest kontrola wydatk\u00f3w oraz elastyczno\u015b\u0107 w dostosowywaniu stawek.<\/p>\n<p><b>Masz wi\u0119cej pyta\u0144? Skontaktuj si\u0119 z nami.<\/b><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<h2>Jak skutecznie zarz\u0105dza\u0107 bud\u017cetem reklamowym w kategorii suplement\u00f3w?<\/h2>\n<p>Czy zastanawia\u0142e\u015b si<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":4772,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"inline_featured_image":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[2],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-4771","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-kontent"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4771"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=4771"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4771\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/4772"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=4771"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?po